There was an eviction of an occupied house, where there were giant parties.
The intruders claimed 11 of the 13 apartments in a building in Balmes, 51
12 occupants left the house yesterday at noon without resisting
All of this suggests that the nightmare that the neighbors of number 51 on Balmes are experiencing is finally over.
Twelve people voluntarily left the building at noon last night, which they were illegally living in, where they organized giant parties that woke up neighbors, leaving the building under court order without having to interfere with the police.
